    "skill2": {
      "name": "Instant Blast",
      "description": "Yin dashes forward, leaving a (Golden Ring) behind while dealing 75( +35% Extra Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to enemies along the way. He gains 30% extra Damage Reduction for 4s if an enemy hero is hit. After 1s, the (Golden Ring) will catch up with Yin, dealing 150( +70% Extra Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to enemies it passes through and stunning them for 1s.",
